Hi Katherine,

Thank you so much for reaching out! Chirag and I would be happy to
participate in the interview. Here are a few times we are available next
week:

   - Monday (1/19): anytime
   - Tuesday (1/20): anytime after 11:00 AM
   - Wednesday (1/21): 10:00 AM - 12:00 PM and 3:00 PM onwards
   - Thursday (1/22): 11:00 AM - 1:00 PM and 2:00pm onwards

Please let us know what time works best for you and we look forward to
meeting with you soon!

Sincerely,
Lizette Wong

